nk ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Ly_giai_nguyen_do_khien_ga_chet_tim_tai\" >L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean do khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Tu_huyet_trung\" >T\u1ee5 huy\u1ebft tr\u00f9ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Dich_cum_gia_cam\" >D\u1ecbch c\u00fam gia c\u1ea7m<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Bo_chet_va_ve\" >B\u1ecd ch\u00e9t v\u00e0 ve<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Ton_thuong_mach_mau\" >T\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Meo_phong_ngua_ga_chet_tim_tai_hieu_qua\" >M\u1eb9o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Ve_sinh_chuong_nuoi_ga\" >V\u1ec7 sinh chu\u1ed3ng nu\u00f4i g\u00e0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Phong_ngua_bang_vacxin\" >Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba b\u1eb1ng vacxin<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Su_dung_thuoc_dac_tri\" >S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Nhung_luu_y_can_biet_khi_ga_co_dau_hieu_tim_tai\" >Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft khi g\u00e0 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-chet-tim-tai\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i>G\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/i><\/a><i> l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi nu\u00f4i g\u00e0, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 anh em nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. H\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam l\u00fd do v\u00e0 m\u1eb9o nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">sv368.direct<\/a>.<\/i><\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ly_giai_nguyen_do_khien_ga_chet_tim_tai\"><\/span><b>L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean do khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 g\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh. <\/span><b>G\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">do \u0111\u00e2u? D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ec7nh g\u00e0 n\u00e0y:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tu_huyet_trung\"><\/span><b>T\u1ee5 huy\u1ebft tr\u00f9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9t nhi\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u00e0u t\u00edm v\u00e0 ch\u1ebft r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111ang b\u1ecb t\u1ee5 huy\u1ebft tr\u00f9ng. B\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y do n\u1ea5m Pasteurella multocida g\u00e2y ra, c\u00f3 trong th\u1ee9c \u0103n v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc u\u1ed1ng cho g\u00e0. G\u00e0 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m b\u1ec7nh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea3y n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf, m\u1ed3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean ph\u1ea3i cho g\u00e0 u\u1ed1ng thu\u1ed1c kh\u00e1ng sinh \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n m\u1ea7m b\u1ec7nh l\u00e2y lan trong \u0111\u00e0n. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh t\u1ee5 huy\u1ebft tr\u00f9ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Kanamicin LG, Hamcoli Forte ho\u1eb7c Gentocostrim \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_cum_gia_cam\"><\/span><b>D\u1ecbch c\u00fam gia c\u1ea7m<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ch\u1ebft g\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i gia c\u1ea7m r\u1ea5t ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn. Khi b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m b\u1ec7nh g\u00e0 c\u00f3 bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 t\u00edm t\u00e1i, ho, h\u1eaft h\u01a1i,.. T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u1eb7ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eed vong \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, b\u1ec7nh c\u00fam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e2y lan r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i qua ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp\u00a0 n\u00ean ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2175\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2175\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2175 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-1.jpg\" alt=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-1.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-1-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-1-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2175\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean do khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bo_chet_va_ve\"><\/span><b>B\u1ecd ch\u00e9t v\u00e0 ve<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ecd ch\u00e9t v\u00e0 ve l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n l\u00e0m <\/span><b>g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m h\u1ee3p v\u1ec7 sinh, s\u1ea1ch nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba b\u1ec7nh t\u00e1i nhi\u1ec5m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ton_thuong_mach_mau\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ebfu g\u00e0 b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng do v\u1eadt s\u1eafc nh\u1ecdn. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho m\u00e0o v\u00e0 y\u1ebfm th\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e0u t\u00edm. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u00ea c\u00f3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm, ng\u01b0\u1eddi nu\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn h\u01a1n khi th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1nh. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, b\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c v\u00e1ch ng\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n gi\u00f3 l\u00f9a v\u00e0o chu\u1ed3ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 anh em b\u00f4i d\u1ea7u l\u00ean y\u1ebfm v\u00e0 m\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u1ea5m v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng t\u00ea c\u00f3ng cho g\u00e0.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2176\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2176\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2176 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-2.jpg\" alt=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-2.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-2-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-2-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2176\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Meo_phong_ngua_ga_chet_tim_tai_hieu_qua\"><\/span><b>M\u1eb9o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 trong ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u00f2ng b\u1ec7nh c\u00f2n h\u01a1n ch\u1eefa b\u1ec7nh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eb9o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba gi\u00fap h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf <\/span><b>g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ve_sinh_chuong_nuoi_ga\"><\/span><b>V\u1ec7 sinh chu\u1ed3ng nu\u00f4i g\u00e0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd khi nu\u00f4i g\u00e0. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, h\u1ee3p v\u1ec7 sinh gi\u00fap n\u00e2ng cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i g\u00e0. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ea7m b\u1ec7nh khi\u1ebfn g\u00e0\u00a0 t\u00edm t\u00e1i v\u00e0 ch\u1ebft th\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb ngu\u1ed3n n\u00e0y.\u00a0 \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f4ng d\u00e2n c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee9c \u0103n, n\u01b0\u1edbc u\u1ed1ng. C\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ea7m b\u1ec7nh c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Phong_ngua_bang_vacxin\"><\/span><b>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba b\u1eb1ng vacxin<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng b\u1ec7nh cho gia c\u1ea7m b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m cho g\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n v\u00e0 cho ph\u00e9p n\u00f3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u1ea7m b\u1ec7nh c\u00e0ng nhanh c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u1eebng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft ch\u00fang c\u00f3 vi-r\u00fat. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a k\u00ea.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Su_dung_thuoc_dac_tri\"><\/span><b>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edm t\u00e1i ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n. Khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng b\u1ec7nh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n d\u1ecbch b\u1ec7nh l\u00e2y lan kh\u1eafp \u0111\u00e0n, g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung thu\u1ed1c cho g\u00e0 trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ch\u0103m s\u00f3c g\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2177\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2177\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2177 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-3.jpg\" alt=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-3.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-3-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-3-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2177\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1eb9o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_luu_y_can_biet_khi_ga_co_dau_hieu_tim_tai\"><\/span><b>Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft khi g\u00e0 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00ean c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 g\u00e0 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o b\u1ec7nh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f4ng d\u00e2n c\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean theo d\u00f5i, c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e0 nu\u00f4i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh <\/span><b>g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu kh\u00ed h\u1eadu qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1nh, v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ea c\u00f3ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Anh em n\u00ean h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng b\u1ec7nh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u1ed1ng g\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch cho g\u00e0 v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba b\u1ec7nh t\u1eadt. V\u00ec v\u1eady, khi ch\u1ecdn g\u00e0,\u00a0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh d\u00e1ng v\u00e0 d\u00e1ng \u0111i c\u1ee7a g\u00e0.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2178\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2178\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2178 size-full\" title=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-4.jpg\" alt=\"g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-4.jpg 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-4-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/ga-chet-tim-tai-4-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2178\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft khi g\u00e0 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 <strong>g\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i<\/strong>. <strong>Sv368<\/strong> hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia s\u1ebb s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra t\u1ea1i trang web c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u tin t\u1ee9c h\u1eefu \u00edch kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc theo d\u00f5i. H\u00e3y \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ngay \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>G\u00e0 ch\u1ebft t\u00edm t\u00e1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i lo ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi nu\u00f4i g\u00e0, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 anh em nu\u00f4i g\u00e0 ch\u1ecdi. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u0103n nu\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. H\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam l\u00fd do v\u00e0 m\u1eb9o [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2177,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2174","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2174","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2174"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2174\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5831,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2174\/revisions\/5831"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2177"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/medi